data.name: btnConveyedItemConnector.ToolTip
data.value:
Get connectors Conveyed Item from selected Element.
1. Select Element 2. Click Button CI Connector (Conveyed Item Connector) 3. EA outputs Search with Source Element of connector 4. Right Click, Find in Diagram 5. EA Shows all Diagrams where the Source Element 6. Explore the diagrams
There is no interface to directly access the connector (as far as I'm aware of)

data.name: btnConveyedItemElement.ToolTip
data.value:
Get Element Conveyed Item from selected Connector
1. Select Connector 2. Click Button CI Element (Conveyed Elements) 3. EA outputs Search with Elements 4. Right Click, Find in Project Browser
There is no interface to directly select more than one Browser Element (as far as I'm aware off)
